Author: miranya
Text: Of course not! I figured this may be the best place to ask (besides an actual doctor) since I am not terribly familiar with eating disorders in general and there may be somebody more knowledgeable here who could say whether the stuff I'm dealing with points at BED at all.  Thank you for your kind words!

Author: linedryonly
Text: Unfortunately, no one here is qualified to diagnose you. But I will say that if you feel that your thoughts or actions related to food/weight/eating are causing you distress, you could probably benefit from talking to a doctor about it.   I'm really sorry you've been struggling and can understand your pain. Whether you have an ED or not, know that you're welcome here and we will be happy to offer support in any way that promotes your health and well-being.
